<sentence id="2">Recombinant transforming growth factor (TGF)-beta was purchased from Peprotech ( London , UK ) .</sentence>
<sentence id="3">Recombinant TNF-alpha and IL-1 were purchased from Endogen Inc. ( Cambridge , MA , USA ) .</sentence>
<sentence id="4">Cyclosporin A was provided by Sandos Ltd. ( Basel , Switzerland ) .</sentence>
<sentence id="5">Phytohemagglutinin ( PHA ) , pyrrolidine dithiocarbamate ( PDTC ) , rapamycin , dexamethasone and curcumin were all obtained from the Sigma Chemical Co. ( St Louis , MA , USA ) .</sentence>
<sentence id="6">Anti-CD3 monoclonal antibody and anti-CD28 monoclonal antibody were obtained from BD Biosciences ( San Diego , CA , USA ) .</sentence>
